- BuildEvents.today is an online platform for corporate event planning.
- It provides an intuitive and customizable way for executives to build the right event.
- It is also a powerful pre-sales tool for the business to capture leads and close deals.
- Built with Next.JS, Django, deployed on GCP

- This project is my entry to Singapore Airlines' SIA App Challenge 2019.
- Avident is a software solution that utilises artificial intelligence technologies such as NLP and machine learning to solve the problems faced by maintenance engineers.
- Built with TypeScript, Ionic Framework and Firebase, deployed as a Progressive Web App for iPads

- A cross-platform Progressive Web App for capturing and storing receipts.
- Receipt information is extracted automatically and can be compiled into a report.
- Built with React JS and MongoDB.

- Designed and implemented an obstacle detection and avoidance algorithm on a Parrot Bebop quadcopter to allow it to fly autonomously in an enclosure.
- Came in 4th out of 11 post-graduate student teams.
- Written in C++ using OpenCV libraries.
